xwikidoc.title: Start XE Web Debug Project
xwikidoc.content:
The first time you start server you have to configure it.
* Right click on web project * Click on //Run As// -> //Run on Server//
image:runweb-1.jpg
----
* Select the server on which to "install" the web project * Click image:DebugXEWithEclipse_Resources@buttonnext.jpg
image:runweb-2.jpg
----
* Click image:DebugXEWithEclipse_Resources@buttonfinish.jpg
image:runweb-3.jpg
When web poject is added to the serveur you will be able to start/stop it simply using //Servers// view.
image:servers.jpg
